Subject: Appliance running on low disk space
Description: I have been receiving alerts from management console that we are running on low disk space.
What_We_Know__c:
the mailer was filling up because the customer had alerts set but no SMTP server configured so all the alerts and emails that needed to be sent were stuck on the server.
We removed all alerts so this should stop using disk space.
Next_Steps__c: monitoring for a few days the mailer
Solution_Comment__c: removing the alerts since there was no SMTP server configured stopped the disk space to fill the mailer
